Commentary: caught at point! Saifuddin digs in another short one, rushing Madhevere, who tries to pull. The ball takes the shoulder of the bat, and balloons on the opposite side as that intended, being easily caught at point. Saifuddin is pumped, and raises his fist at the young Zimbabwean to send him off. The visitors had just started to find some traction with this stand, but it's been broken now, and Bangladesh are well on top
